generic method return parameter : House <? super Dog>
has super type realtionship with
House<Dog>, House<Animal>, House<Object>, House<>

type class parameter : <A extends Animal>
following types are within bounds of type-varaible A. And it allows :
House<Dog>, House<Animal>, House<Predog>, House<>

